  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 3022234210304
    m_Localized: OK!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 145428205568
    m_Localized: You've got a great merchant. This week's sales buffs will be activated!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 233265319936
    m_Localized: The facility inspection period is back. During this week, the maintenance
      costs of the building will temporarily increase.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 451708866560
    m_Localized: The Village Festival begins! All cases' sales go up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 549507452928
    m_Localized: What a thriving town! There is a huge increase in the chances of
      high-tier visitors coming.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 670173384704
    m_Localized: The base is open normally! Now visitors are coming!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 834766262272
    m_Localized: Village Operations Are Back on a Steady Track! The volume of goods
      acquired increases.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 915020075008
    m_Localized: It's been rumored among adventurers! Visitors are increasing this
      week.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1002764914688
    m_Localized: It has gained worldwide fame! The legendary warrior is visiting!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1152056971264
    m_Localized: "The Village Has Grown! The construction of the new building [caf\xE9]
      has been unlocked."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1210689146880
    m_Localized: "Customers want a better store. [Caf\xE9] can be upgraded to level
      2."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1256037961728
    m_Localized: "Customers want a better store. [Caf\xE9] can be upgraded to level
      3."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1417275396096
    m_Localized: Don't spare your investment! [Hot Spring Level 2] Upgrade and new
      building [Restaurant] has been lifted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1543951765504
    m_Localized: Don't spare your investment! [Hot Spring] Level 3 upgrade has been
      lifted,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2022362468352
    m_Localized: Customers want a better restaurant. You can upgrade your [restaurant]
      to level 2!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2103924903936
    m_Localized: Let's sell various items. The construction of the new building [store]
      has been unlocked.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2182870093824
    m_Localized: Professional services are available! [Store] Level 2 upgrades and
      [Restaurant] Level 3 upgrades have been lifted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2710362542080
    m_Localized: Professional service is available! [Shop] Level 3 upgrade is lifted!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2797713117184
    m_Localized: You can get a powerful adventurer as a guest! [Training ground]
      is newly released!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2847101046784
    m_Localized: More adventurer visits! [Training ground] Level 2 upgrades lifted!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2900247072768
    m_Localized: Word of mouth has spread among adventurers! [Training ground] Level
      3 upgrade is lifted!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
